Totally Outsourced Ltd provide essential services to Wapo y Wapa Limited including app development and maintenance of servers and database and therefore require access to your data. Totally Outsourced Ltd agree to abide by the exact same Privacy Policy as Wapo y Wapa Limited. At all times, your data will remain under the control of Wapo y Wapa Limited
